S magnetic field and the coherence\nlength. We also consider the turbulent magnetic field modeled with power-law\nspectrum, and study how the magnetic field is revealed in Faraday spectrum. Our\nwork suggests a way toward obtaining the information of magnetic field from\nFaraday tomography study.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Jan 2017 04:51:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Jun 2017 01:32:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
