 origin for Hildas and Trojans as predicted by\ncurrent dynamical instability theories of Solar System evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Jan 2017 11:50:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-18"}
